@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_goipcq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.65 + v0 + 0.38)) / 0.61)
    v1 = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.08 * v2 + 0.92) - 0.93))
    tmp = wp.abs((v0 + (v2 + 0.09 + tmp + 0.01)))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.exp(v1))
    data[tid] = v0
